'From Squeak2.7 of 5 January 2000 [latest update: #1789] on 5 February 2000 at 12:49:21 pm'!"Change Set:		BoldBinarySelectors-dewDate:			30 December 1999Author:			Doug WayThis fixes browser method text panes so that binary selectors are displayed as bold, just like unary and keyword selectors."!!Text methodsFor: 'emphasis' stamp: 'sma 2/5/2000 12:03'!makeSelectorBoldIn: aClass	"For formatting Smalltalk source code, set the emphasis of that portion of 	the receiver's string that parses as a message selector to be bold."	| parser |	string size = 0 ifTrue: [^self].	(parser _ aClass parserClass new) parseSelector: string.	self makeBoldFrom: 1 to: (parser endOfLastToken min: string size)! !